# AI Personal Email Assistant

## Features
- Gmail API integration
- GPT-4 summarization
- Slack alerting
- Google Calendar scheduling
- Web search (Bing)
- Vercel-ready FastAPI backend

## Setup
- Configure `.env` with Gmail, OpenAI, Slack, Bing credentials
- Run locally with `uvicorn api.main:app --reload`
- Deploy using `vercel --prod`

## Architecture
Emails → Gmail API → GPT Summary → Slack / Calendar → Reply
